{"database_schema": ""Description for table: BridgeWithdrawalTransaction"
type BridgeWithdrawalTransaction implements Transaction @entity {
  "Unique identifier for the transaction"
  id: ID!
  "Block number in which the transaction was included"
  blockNumber: Int!
  "Timestamp of when the transaction occurred"
  timestamp: Int!
  "Account that signed the transaction"
  signer: GraphAccount!
  "Type of the transaction"
  type: TransactionType!
  "Hash of the transaction"
  txHash: Bytes
  "Address from which the transaction was sent"
  from: Bytes
  "Address to which the transaction was sent"
  to: Bytes
  "Amount involved in the transaction"
  amount: BigInt
  "Token on Layer 1 involved in the transaction"
  l1Token: Bytes
  "Index of the transaction within the block"
  transactionIndex: BigInt
}"}
